<p class="ayah 46-32" id="32" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And whoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(does) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُجِبْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">respond</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دَاعِىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to the) caller</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَيْسَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمُعْجِزٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he can escape</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَرْضِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the earth,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَيْسَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن دُونِهِۦٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">besides Him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="r